{"tid":1102592,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"罪大惡極的Animal Eye AF測試","createTime":"2019-04-11T22:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T02:09:18.000Z","uid":247977,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"925196ba3405385a079bbec65eb70ae60b1a8ee3","tid":1102592,"uid":247977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T22:34:46.000Z","msg":"尋日一出左我已經等唔切飛車去左動物園測試<br />\n用過之後真係覺得罪大惡極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頂你可以用1.4光圈將動物當人像影<br />\n而且好多動物都可以。尋日試左由豹到袋鼠樹熊，紅熊貓，甚至四腳爬爬的都無問題 (不過下方扑野中的烏龜係唔得的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n不過有幾個地方用的時候要注意:<br />\n1. 被影的眼唔可以太細.....當然你close up埋去無問題。但當影全身時，影Koala有時搵唔到眼；影Emu同箭豬唔得，仲有扑野中的水箭龜都搵唔到眼。<br />\n<br />\n2. 最好有七三面入鏡。半邊面唔係時時搵到眼<br />\n<br />\n3. 小心一啲形狀似眼的暗位會被認左做眼。尋日試過影山羊，佢認左隻耳係眼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsuL24d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsuL24d.jpg&h=f01c8019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mo6Zn0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMo6Zn0C.jpg&h=ad761b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJ3AFNu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJ3AFNu.jpg&h=349a6d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvBuLer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvBuLer.jpg&h=f5f47545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANNYDzL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANNYDzL.jpg&h=982c8138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oMROgmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoMROgmK.jpg&h=0a46f029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJ1Ky8H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/